is campaigning in Colorado.

02:36.327 --> 02:41.242
The Warren Commission, almost a full
year after the Kennedy assassination...

02:43.047 --> 02:46.198
- Glenn, it's time.
- No, just a little more.

02:46.287 --> 02:50.326
If you don't get up right now,
I'm gonna cut one of your piano strings.

02:50.407 --> 02:52.318
Ugh...

02:52.407 --> 02:54.762
- What time is it?
- Quarter to seven.

02:55.727 --> 02:58.321
- A quarter to seven!
- Mm-hm.

02:58.407 --> 03:00.398
Oh, God.

03:01.247 --> 03:03.397
Does the sun really come out this early?

03:03.487 --> 03:08.163
It was a surprise to me, too. I took
a picture in case it never happens again.

03:08.247 --> 03:12.320
- Nobody gets up this early.
- Oh, yes, they do.

03:12.407 --> 03:16.082
Come on, come on, come on.
Please, please, please, please, please!

03:16.167 --> 03:19.842
- Come on, come on, come on, come on.
- No, no, no! This is a stupid idea.

03:19.927 --> 03:22.646
Oh, this is definitely not my scene, Iris.

03:23.287 --> 03:27.166
It's just a gig. If it doesn't work,
you can try something else.

03:27.927 --> 03:30.760
- What time am I supposed to be there?
- 7.30.

03:30.847 --> 03:32.838
7.30!

03:33.447 --> 03:37.565
What kind of people like to
go to work at 7.30 in the morning?

03:37.647 --> 03:39.717
(~ `One, Two, Three` by Len Barry)

03:45.887 --> 03:47.878
~ One, two, three

03:49.527 --> 03:52.564
